@startuml
title virtio-gpu DRM stack with real files and functions

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam monochrome true
autonumber

participant "QEMU\nhw/display/virtio-gpu-pci.c" as QEMUPCI
participant "QEMU\nhw/virtio/virtio-pci.c" as VirtioPCICore
participant "QEMU\nhw/display/virtio-gpu.c" as QEMUGPU
participant "Linux PCI core" as PCICore
participant "virtio_pci\n(kernel driver)" as VirtioPCI
participant "virtio core\n(kernel driver)" as VirtioCore
participant "virtio_gpu\n(kernel DRM driver)" as VirtioGPU
participant "DRM core\n(kernel DRM subsystem)" as DRMCore
participant "libdrm\noutput/build/libdrm-2.4.131/xf86drm.c" as LibDRM
participant "modetest\noutput/build/libdrm-2.4.131/tests/modetest/modetest.c" as Modetest
participant "kms.c\noutput/build/libdrm-2.4.131/tests/util/kms.c" as KMS

== Boot / probe ==
QEMUPCI -> VirtioPCICore : virtio_gpu_pci_base_realize()\n(hw/display/virtio-gpu-pci.c)
VirtioPCICore -> QEMUGPU : virtio_pci_realize()\n(hw/virtio/virtio-pci.c)
QEMUGPU -> QEMUGPU : virtio_gpu_device_realize()\n(hw/display/virtio-gpu.c)
QEMUGPU -> QEMUGPU : set up virtio queues / scanouts
QEMUGPU -> PCICore : PCI device visible to guest
PCICore -> VirtioPCI : kernel probe/bind
VirtioPCI -> VirtioCore : virtio transport setup
VirtioCore -> VirtioGPU : virtio_gpu kernel probe
VirtioGPU -> DRMCore : drm_dev_init()\ndrm_dev_register()
DRMCore --> VirtioGPU : /dev/dri/card0 created\nconnector / crtc / plane registered

== User space open ==
Modetest -> KMS : main() -> util_open(module="virtio_gpu")
KMS -> LibDRM : drmOpen(module, device)\n(or open /dev/dri/card0)
LibDRM -> LibDRM : drmOpenByName()\ndrmOpenDevice()\ndrmGetVersion()
LibDRM --> KMS : fd + version->name = "virtio_gpu"

== Query DRM objects ==
Modetest -> Modetest : get_resources(&dev)
Modetest -> DRMCore : drmSetClientCap(DRM_CLIENT_CAP_UNIVERSAL_PLANES)
Modetest -> DRMCore : drmModeGetResources()\ndrmModeGetPlaneResources()
Modetest -> DRMCore : drmModeObjectGetProperties()\ndrmModeGetProperty()
DRMCore --> Modetest : connectors / CRTCs / planes / props

== Parse and resolve -s ==
Modetest -> Modetest : parse_connector("38@37:1024x768")
Modetest -> Modetest : pipe_args{cons="38", crtc_id=37,\nmode_str="1024x768", format_str="XR24"}
Modetest -> Modetest : pipe_resolve_connectors()\npipe_find_crtc_and_mode()

== Modeset ==
Modetest -> Modetest : set_mode(&dev, &pipe_args, count)
Modetest -> Modetest : connector_find_mode(38, "1024x768")
Modetest -> Modetest : bo_fb_create()\ncreate dumb buffer + drmModeAddFB2()
Modetest -> DRMCore : drmModeSetCrtc(fd, 37, fb_id, ...)\nlegacy path
DRMCore -> VirtioGPU : atomic/legacy KMS commit\nscanout update
VirtioGPU -> QEMUGPU : host visible framebuffer update
QEMUGPU --> Modetest : SDL window shows the image

note right of Modetest
Important functions in modetest.c
- main()
- parse_connector()
- get_resources()
- set_mode()
- connector_find_mode()
- pipe_find_crtc_and_mode()
end note

note right of KMS
Important functions in kms.c / xf86drm.c
- util_open()
- drmOpen()
- drmOpenByName()
- drmOpenDevice()
- drmGetVersion()
end note

@enduml
